      "description": {
        "text": "=General= A pleasant area with varying rock quality. There is a very long overhanging project located here. =Access= Drive along road 72 towards Sala, turn left towards the Fornborg after Västerby. The boulders are located below the fort on the south side. Approximately 500 m walk from the parking.",
